author: Amber Phillips
title: What you need to know from Wednesday’s White House coronavirus briefing
description: Trump didn't deny that the U.S. thinks the virus came from a Wuhan virology lab.
content: On Tuesday, Washington Post opinion columnist Josh Rogin reported that the State Department was very concerned about a Wuhan labs safety protocols as it studied coronavirus in bats. Rogin said diplomats wrote cables in early 2018 warning that the labs work on… [+5053 chars]
